Recently, a video of "Audi owner angrily scolding traffic police" went viral on the Internet. Later, some netizens believed that this person was Harbin Deputy Mayor Tan Lewei based on the license plate and facial features. Later, some media said that the man was just a worker and the car was bought by his father.
However, on May 27, a blogger posted that a man was detained for 15 days by the Fendou Road Police Station in Nangang District, Harbin for "picking quarrels and provoking trouble" because he commented "This is the deputy mayor" under the video.
